name: THESINS//006 : THE LONELY HOUR
description:
ACT//006. NORTH HOUSE SCENE. 

When night falls, sometimes the emptiness inside began to emerge and dominate. Anxiety & restlessness which always haunt, defeated by a sense of loneliness that is inside.
“Carl hasn't been home for a week.” May told everyone. She saw them talking, muttering, but her mind was frantic, she didn’t even listen.
suddenly her phone rang. Tom's name appeared. everyone was silent and watched May.
